PrecisAMI - DEPATTERNED PERSONS ASSISTANCE ORDER - which authorizes the Minister of Justice to make ex gratia payments of $100,000 to patients of Dr. Ewen Cameron who received full or substantial depatterning treatment at the Allan Memorial Institute in Montreal between the years 1950 and 1965.

AMI - DEPATTERNED PERSONS ASSISTANCE ORDER - which authorizes the Minister
of Justice to make ex gratia payments of $100,000 to patients of Dr. Ewen
Cameron who received full or substantial depatterning treatment at the
Allan Memorial Institute in Montreal between the years 1950 and 1965.
